## Design Considerations

### Design System Compliance
- **Colors:** Accent-blue for current date, accent-cyan for event dots, neutral backgrounds
- **Components:** Widget wrapper, minimal buttons, clean grid layout
- **Typography:** text-xs for dates, text-sm for headers
- **Spacing:** gap-1 between day cells, p-1 cell padding
- **Dark Mode:** Automatic via color tokens (surface-light/dark, text-light/dark)

### Performance
- **Bundle Size Impact:** +5-10KB (compact widget ~200 lines)
- **Lazy Loading:** No (calendar widget part of dashboard, always loaded)
- **Optimization:** Memoize event count calculation

### Accessibility
- **Keyboard Nav:** Tab through dates, Enter to navigate
- **Screen Reader:** Announce date + event count ("January 17, 3 events")
- **Focus Management:** Clear focus states on date buttons

