## Implementation Notes

### Decisions Made
- 2025-01-17 - Chose Option A (Dual Modes) based on user approval and industry research
- 2025-01-17 - Used `calendarmini` as widget ID to avoid conflict with existing calendar
- 2025-01-17 - Set `defaultEnabled: true` for immediate visibility

### Challenges Encountered
- 2025-01-17 - TypeScript errors with date utility functions
  - Solution: Functions take Date objects, not separate year/month/day parameters
  - Fixed by creating Date objects before calling utility functions
- 2025-01-17 - Widget component doesn't accept `size` prop
  - Solution: Removed size prop, Widget handles sizing via grid layout

